1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:02,400
The lead role for the school festival...

2
00:00:03,720 --> 00:00:06,120
You always look so lifeless.

3
00:00:07,040 --> 00:00:09,240
This is our last school festival in high school.

4
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:11,920
You really are a bratty little brother.

5
00:00:12,840 --> 00:00:14,800
Besides,

6
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:15,840
Mizuki, you...

7
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:19,200
Weren't you quite cheerful back in middle school?

8
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:24,720
I don't know what happened to you,

9
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,600
but you shouldn't suppress your true self.

10
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:32,760
My true self...

11
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:40,640
I can't believe those words came out of your mouth.

12
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:45,320
You two! It's time to start practice!

13
00:00:45,900 --> 00:00:47,000
(Class 3-A: Cinderella)

14
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:50,520
Go into town and find

15
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:53,320
the girl who can fit into this glass slipper.

16
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:55,280
Leave it to me,
my Prince.

17
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:57,480
The Prince was deeply captivated by Cinderella.

18
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:01,600
Using the glass slipper she left behind,

19
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:04,680
he ordered his servants to find her.

20
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:09,120
Could she be the one the Prince is looking for?

21
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:10,680
Your Highness!

22
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:12,600
The shoe fits perfectly!

23
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:18,360
Oh my! The Prince has found me!

24
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:20,880
Cinderella.

25
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:24,000
Prince! Please, give me the kiss of true love!

26
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,920
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

27
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:29,320
I see. So if he plays the lead,

28
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:32,040
he ends up with Cinderella.

29
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:35,240
Whatever, it's no big deal...

30
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,560
It's just a play, after all.

31
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,840
Mizuki! Your acting was amazing!

32
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,320
Yeah!

33
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:42,040
You were really impressive.

34
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,040
That was a fantastic performance!

35
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,680
As long as he looks happy, that's all that matters!
